title: (Mon Early Bird) Dierks Bentley and Elle King Perform Their New Duet + Bobby’s 2 Truths and A Lie Game + Mailbag: Who Should Pay for the Wedding?
itunes:title: (Mon Early Bird) Dierks Bentley and Elle King Perform Their New Duet + Bobby’s 2 Truths and A Lie Game + Mailbag: Who Should Pay for the Wedding?
description:
Dierks Bentley and Elle King stop by to perform their new duet “Worth a Shot”. They talk about their first collaboration “Different for Girls”, how they met and hosting CMA Music Fest together. Bobby gives a caller 3 statements and they have to guess which one is the lie. In the mailbag, a listener wants to know if her parents should be forced to pay for her wedding just because of tradition.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
